{"text_id":199514,"tokens":["We"," investigate"," the"," intriguing"," possibility"," of"," simultaneous"," existence"," of"," massive"," and"," massless"," neutrinos"," in"," the"," framework"," of"," unbalanced"," sees","aws","."," Our"," motivation"," stems"," from"," the"," observation"," that"," the"," traditional"," type","-","I"," sees","aw"," mechanism",","," which"," elegantly"," explains"," the"," small","ness"," of"," neutrino"," masses",","," relies"," on"," a"," delicate"," balance"," between"," the"," neutrino"," Yu","kawa"," couplings"," and"," the"," heavy"," Major","ana"," mass"," scale","."," We"," challenge"," this"," balance"," by"," introducing"," a"," novel"," scenario",","," where"," the"," sees","aw"," is"," intentionally"," unbalanced",","," resulting"," in"," a"," unique"," coexistence"," of"," massive"," and"," massless"," neutrino"," states","."," Our"," methodology"," involves"," a"," comprehensive"," analysis"," of"," the"," neutrino"," mass"," matrix",","," incorporating"," both"," the"," flavor"," and"," the"," sterile"," sectors","."," By"," employing"," a"," systematic"," perturb","ative"," approach",","," we"," derive"," the"," Conditions"," for"," the"," emergence"," of"," massless"," neutrinos"," and"," explore"," their"," phenomen","ological"," implications","."," Our"," results"," reveal"," that"," the"," unbalanced"," sees","aw"," scenario"," can"," accommodate"," the"," observed"," neutrino"," oscillation"," data",","," while"," also"," providing"," a"," natural"," explanation"," for"," the"," absence"," of"," a"," signal"," in"," neutr","inol","ess"," double"," beta"," decay"," experiments","."," We"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," massless"," neutrino"," states"," can"," have"," significant"," repercussions"," for"," cosmology",","," particle"," physics",","," and"," the"," search"," for"," beyond"," the"," Standard"," Model"," physics","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}